FORM F_PRINT1.

  SORT I_RESB1 BY LGORT.

  LOOP AT I_RESB1.

    PERFORM F_COR_LINHA.

    WRITE: / I_RESB1-LGORT UNDER TEXT-006,
             I_RESB1-MATNR UNDER TEXT-005,
             I_RESB1-QTDE UNDER TEXT-011.

  ENDLOOP.

ENDFORM.                               "F_PRINT1
